issue.body:
I have two projects:

 - a class library project using `IDesignTimeDbContextFactory` as follows:

<!-------->

    class Program : IDesignTimeDbContextFactory<TheContext>
    {
        public TheContext CreateDbContext(string[] args)
        {
            IConfiguration config = new ConfigurationBuilder()
                                        .AddUserSecrets<MyUserSecrets.Empty>()
                                        .Build();

            string connectionString = config.GetConnectionString("Duplicate");

            string assemblyName = Assembly.GetAssembly(typeof(MigrationTarget.Empty))!
                                          .GetName()
                                          .Name!;

            var dcob = new DbContextOptionsBuilder<TheContext>()
                            .UseSqlServer(connectionString, ssdcob => ssdcob.MigrationsAssembly(assemblyName));


            return new(dcob.Options);
        }
    }



- a console application project as follows:

```
Host.CreateDefaultBuilder()
    .ConfigureHostConfiguration(icb => icb.AddUserSecrets<MyUserSecrets.Empty>())
    .ConfigureServices((hbc, isc) =>
    {
        isc.AddDbContext<TheContext>(dcob =>
        {
            string connectionString = hbc.Configuration.GetConnectionString("Duplicate");

            string assemblyName = Assembly.GetAssembly(typeof(MigrationTarget.Empty))!
                                          .GetName()
                                          .Name!;

            dcob.UseSqlServer(connectionString, ssdcob => ssdcob.MigrationsAssembly(assemblyName));
        });
    })
    .Build();
```

When I invoke `update-database`, the former project produces fewer logs compared to the latter project.

former:

```
PM> update-database
Build started...
Build succeeded.
Applying migration '20220325084814_Initialization'.
Done.
```

latter:

```
PM> update-database
Build started...
Build succeeded.
Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Infrastructure[10403]
      Entity Framework Core 6.0.3 initialized 'TheContext' using provider 'Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer:6.0.3' with options: MigrationsAssembly=MigrationTarget 

........ trimmed because too long ............

Done.
```

### Question

What causes this difference?
